# Kali Linux & OverTheWire Bandit Walkthrough

## Kali Linux Installation

### VirtualBox Setup
- Download VirtualBox from virtualbox.org
- Download Kali Linux from kali.org (VirtualBox pre-built image recommended)
- Import appliance: File → Import Appliance → Select .ova file
- Default credentials: kali / kali

### Post-Installation Commands

sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y
sudo apt install net-tools wireshark nmap -y
